snippet.title: Live Coding: React Native Mobile App w/ Django REST Framework (GPS bookmarker)
snippet.description:
Let's take the skills we've learned in the previous week with React, React Native, and Django REST Framework to create a mobile front end and a REST API backend. We'll continue the project we've been building of the GPS bookmarker.

GitHub: https://www.github.com/DevDungeon
Support the stream: https://streamlabs.com/devdungeon
